videos.description: Scottie Lindsey drains a transition triple and the Northwestern bench gets fired up as the Wildcats lead the Spartans 20-6.

videos.description: Gavin Skelly drives hard to the hoop for the bucket and a foul as Northwestern takes a 42-16 lead over Michigan State.
videos.headline: Skelly's and-1 increases No. 2 MSU's deficit

videos.description: After a stolen inbounds pass, Vic Law pushes the ball up to Anthony Gaines who launches for a thunderous dunk.

videos.description: Jaren Jackson Jr. gets the pass in space under the basket and slams it home with two hands to cut the Spartans' deficit to 19.
videos.headline: Jackson trying to mount MSU comeback

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One-Play (Jackson trying to mount MSU comeback) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: Jaren Jackson Jr. gets the ball in the low post and scores from there to give the Spartans their first lead over Northwestern at 55-53.
videos.headline: Spartans take first lead after trailing by 22

videos.description: Michigan State comes roaring back in the second half and ties the game at 53 after Nick Ward's putback.
